room_title: Escape room "Laboratory of Biohazard" by OMEscape in New York
room_description: NYPD just got intel that Dr. Snake's secret laboratory is located in the sewage system of the city. The source says he has been working on a new neurotoxin which may poison thousands of people if released. The process is already started, and in 60 minutes the damage will be irreversible. You are the city's last hope - locate the lab and find a cure for the toxin!
